    "Terms like laparoscopy or endoscopy might appear in both contexts but would need clarification, as they could refer to diagnostic procedures without any resection or obstruction.",
    "MAJOR -DIABETES: Associated with meeting the criterion of having a history of diabetes and major diabetes -related complications, words might include hyperglycemia, insulin, type 1 diabetes, type 2 diabetes, HbA1c, diabetic neuropathy, retinopathy, diabetic foot ulcer, nephropathy, cardiovascu lar disease, stroke, myocardial infarction, peripheral artery disease, and end -stage renal disease.",
